1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
In Pęgów,
we are not afraid
of fires.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:08,000
We have
experienced firefighters.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:12,000
The local fire unit
was created

4
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:16,000
right after
World War II.

5
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:20,000
Back then,
war damage
was everywhere.

6
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:24,000
It was very hard
to get equipment.

7
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:28,000
Luckily,
an old horse-drawn
fire pump survived.

8
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,000
Thanks to it,
firefighters
began helping people.

9
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:36,000
Even with
very simple tools.

10
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:40,000
Over time,
the unit grew
stronger.

11
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:44,000
It improved
when taken over

12
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:48,000
by a state farm.

13
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:52,000
But the building
was still not great.

14
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:56,000
The fire station
was in this building.

15
00:00:56,000 --> 00:01:00,000
In the video,
we see it
after renovation.

16
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:04,000
The renovation happened
in the 1990s.

17
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:08,000
In 2014,
firefighters moved

18
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:12,000
to a new,
big, modern station.

19
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:16,000
Now they leave
from there

20
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:20,000
to fight fires

21
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:26,000
and help people
where it is needed most.